  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Adwaita Icon Theme</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Adwaita Icon Theme</application> package contains
      an assortment of non-scalable icons of different sizes and themes.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&adwaita-icon-theme-download-http;"/>
